{"id": "题目-1442-gpt5.4-sample-1", "name": "_1442__gpt5.4__sample_1", "description": "", "category": "gui", "query": "", "steps": [{"id": 0, "action_type": "wait", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-sample-1/1.webp", "action_value_1": [], "thought": "当前桌面空闲，未见 OpenPLC Editor 已启动。我需要先打开终端并按给定脚本路径启动 OpenPLC Editor，这样才能创建项目、编写 LD 梯形图并进行仿真。"}, {"id": 1, "action_type": "hotkey", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-sample-1/2.webp", "action_value_1": ["ctrl alt t"], "thought": "桌面仍是空闲状态。直接用快捷键打开终端最快，然后执行题目指定的启动命令。"}, {"id": 2, "action_type": "move", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-sample-1/3.webp", "action_value_1": [32, 1042], "thought": "快捷键没有明显打开终端，我改用应用列表搜索“Terminal”，这是更稳妥的启动方式。"}, {"id": 3, "action_type": "type", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-sample-1/4.webp", "action_value_1": "sh ", "thought": "终端已打开，我现在按题目给定路径运行 OpenPLC Editor 启动脚本。"}, {"id": 4, "action_type": "move", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-sample-1/5.webp", "action_value_1": [35, 406], "thought": "命令没有输入到终端，而是误进了系统搜索界面。我先回到终端，再重新执行启动命令。"}, {"id": 5, "action_type": "type", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-sample-1/6.webp", "action_value_1": "sh ", "thought": "我已回到终端，改用整段单引号包裹路径，避免空格导致路径解析错误。"}, {"id": 6, "action_type": "type", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-sample-1/7.webp", "action_value_1": "find /home/user/Downloads -maxdepth 4 -iname ", "thought": "给定命令里的文件名似乎与实际不完全一致。我先在 Downloads 下查找 OpenPLC 相关文件，定位正确的启动脚本。"}, {"id": 7, "action_type": "type", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-sample-1/8.webp", "action_value_1": "sh /home/user/Downloads/OpenPLC_Editor/OpenPLC_Editor/openplc_editor.sh", "thought": "已找到实际安装目录，实际脚本名是 `openplc_editor.sh`。我现在用找到的真实路径启动编辑器。"}, {"id": 8, "action_type": "type", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-sample-1/9.webp", "action_value_1": "sed -n ", "thought": "脚本用 `sh` 启动失败，报错显示它更像是按 bash 和固定目录编写的。我先查看脚本内容和目录结构，再用正确方式启动。"}, {"id": 9, "action_type": "type", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-sample-1/10.webp", "action_value_1": "ls -la /home/user/Downloads/OpenPLC_Editor/OpenPLC_Editor && ls -la /home/user/Downloads/OpenPLC_Editor/OpenPLC_Editor/.venv/bin | head && ls -la /home/user/Downloads/OpenPLC_Editor/OpenPLC_Editor/editor | head", "thought": "脚本首行和硬编码目录都有问题。更可靠的做法是检查实际目录内的虚拟环境和主程序，然后直接从正确目录运行。"}, {"id": 10, "action_type": "type", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-sample-1/11.webp", "action_value_1": "cd /home/user/Downloads/OpenPLC_Editor/OpenPLC_Editor && ./.venv/bin/python3 ./editor/Beremiz.py", "thought": "实际目录中 `.venv` 和 `editor/Beremiz.py` 都存在，我直接在该目录下用内置 Python 启动编辑器主程序。"}, {"id": 11, "action_type": "wait", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-sample-1/12.webp", "action_value_1": [], "thought": "编辑器正在从 Python 主程序启动，我等待窗口出现。"}, {"id": 12, "action_type": "move", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-sample-1/13.webp", "action_value_1": [102, 111], "thought": "OpenPLC Editor 已打开，下一步先新建项目并把工程保存到题目要求的输出路径。"}, {"id": 13, "action_type": "move", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-sample-1/14.webp", "action_value_1": [91, 75], "thought": "工具栏点击没有明显弹窗，我改用菜单栏的 File 新建，通常更稳定。"}, {"id": 14, "action_type": "move", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-sample-1/15.webp", "action_value_1": [369, 227], "thought": "现在是新建工程目录选择框。我需要进入 Desktop 下的 output，并新建空目录 `Case1_Motor` 作为项目根目录。"}, {"id": 15, "action_type": "move", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-sample-1/16.webp", "action_value_1": [522, 282], "thought": "桌面里同时有 `Output` 和 `output`，题目要求的是小写 `output`，我进入小写目录。"}, {"id": 16, "action_type": "move", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-sample-1/17.webp", "action_value_1": [1226, 154], "thought": "`output` 目录是空的，符合要求。我现在在其中创建 `Case1_Motor` 文件夹。"}, {"id": 17, "action_type": "type", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-sample-1/18.webp", "action_value_1": "Case1_Motor", "thought": "已弹出新建文件夹输入框，我输入项目目录名 `Case1_Motor`。"}, {"id": 18, "action_type": "move", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-sample-1/19.webp", "action_value_1": [1205, 102], "thought": "现在路径已经是 `/home/user/Desktop/output/Case1_Motor`，我确认用这个空目录创建项目。"}, {"id": 19, "action_type": "type", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-sample-1/20.webp", "action_value_1": "Main", "thought": "项目标题已经是 `Case1_Motor`。现在在建 POU 对话框中把程序名设为 `Main`，类型保持 `program`，语言改为 `LD`。"}, {"id": 20, "action_type": "move", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-sample-1/21.webp", "action_value_1": [775, 592], "thought": "语言下拉列表已打开，我选择 LD 梯形图语言并确认创建。"}, {"id": 21, "action_type": "move", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-sample-1/22.webp", "action_value_1": [147, 214], "thought": "`Main` 已创建，接下来打开它，进入 LD 编辑区并设置变量和梯形图。"}, {"id": 22, "action_type": "move", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-sample-1/23.webp", "action_value_1": [1098, 183], "thought": "进入 `Main` 的 LD 编辑器了。先在上方变量表中添加 3 个 BOOL 变量，再绘制起保停梯形图。"}, {"id": 23, "action_type": "move", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-sample-1/24.webp", "action_value_1": [464, 255], "thought": "变量表已新增一行默认变量。我先把第一行改成 `Start_PB`，并把类型从 DINT 改成 BOOL。"}, {"id": 24, "action_type": "type", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-sample-1/25.webp", "action_value_1": "Start_PB", "thought": "名称单元格已进入编辑状态，我直接输入目标变量名。"}, {"id": 25, "action_type": "move", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-sample-1/26.webp", "action_value_1": [618, 255], "thought": "第一行名称已改好，接下来把类型从默认的 DINT 改成 BOOL。"}, {"id": 26, "action_type": "move", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-sample-1/27.webp", "action_value_1": [750, 256], "thought": "类型菜单已经打开，我从基础类型里选择 BOOL。"}, {"id": 27, "action_type": "move", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-sample-1/28.webp", "action_value_1": [748, 257], "thought": "这是级联菜单，我把鼠标移到 Base Types 上以展开基础类型列表。"}, {"id": 28, "action_type": "move", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-sample-1/29.webp", "action_value_1": [881, 257], "thought": "菜单还没展开，我点击 Base Types 右侧箭头来展开具体基础类型。"}, {"id": 29, "action_type": "hotkey", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-sample-1/30.webp", "action_value_1": ["right"], "thought": "级联菜单还没显现，我用方向键展开子菜单。"}, {"id": 30, "action_type": "move", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-sample-1/31.webp", "action_value_1": [944, 257], "thought": "基础类型列表已展开，我选择 BOOL。"}, {"id": 31, "action_type": "move", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-sample-1/32.webp", "action_value_1": [1097, 182], "thought": "第一行变量已正确设置为 `Start_PB : BOOL`。我继续添加 `Stop_PB` 和 `Motor`。"}, {"id": 32, "action_type": "type", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-sample-1/33.webp", "action_value_1": "Stop_PB", "thought": "新增行自动沿用了前一个变量名并编号，我把它们分别改成 `Stop_PB` 和 `Motor`。"}, {"id": 33, "action_type": "move", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-sample-1/34.webp", "action_value_1": [880, 109], "thought": "变量已基本就位。现在我先识别 LD 工具栏中的母线、触点、线圈等元件按钮，再按题目指定结构搭建起保停回路。"}, {"id": 34, "action_type": "move", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-sample-1/35.webp", "action_value_1": [921, 110], "thought": "母线按钮已确认。继续识别后面的触点和线圈按钮，避免选错元件。"}, {"id": 35, "action_type": "move", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-sample-1/36.webp", "action_value_1": [992, 109], "thought": "最后一个按钮是连接线工具。现在逐个确认前面的触点和线圈工具。"}, {"id": 36, "action_type": "move", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-sample-1/37.webp", "action_value_1": [922, 109], "thought": "这个按钮不是线圈，而是“新建变量”。继续确认前两个接点样式按钮。"}, {"id": 37, "action_type": "move", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-sample-1/38.webp", "action_value_1": [920, 109], "thought": "这个按钮是“新建触点”。我再确认左边那个是不是线圈。"}, {"id": 38, "action_type": "move", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-sample-1/39.webp", "action_value_1": [882, 108], "thought": "工具类型已识别。我先在梯形图区放置一根母线，确认 OpenPLC 的放置方式和默认属性。"}, {"id": 39, "action_type": "move", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-sample-1/40.webp", "action_value_1": [858, 543], "thought": "母线属性窗口出现了。按题意先保留为 Left PowerRail、1 个引脚并确认。"}, {"id": 40, "action_type": "move", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-sample-1/41.webp", "action_value_1": [958, 109], "thought": "左母线已放好。接着在其右侧放置第一个触点，并确认触点属性的设置入口。"}, {"id": 41, "action_type": "move", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-sample-1/42.webp", "action_value_1": [750, 531], "thought": "触点属性对话框已打开。这个触点需要设为常开 Normal，并把变量指定为 `Start_PB`。"}, {"id": 42, "action_type": "move", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-sample-1/43.webp", "action_value_1": [698, 599], "thought": "变量列表已展开，我选择 `Start_PB` 并确认。"}, {"id": 43, "action_type": "move", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-sample-1/44.webp", "action_value_1": [958, 109], "thought": "第一个启动触点已放置。现在在其右侧放置停止触点，并把 Modifier 设为 Negated。"}, {"id": 44, "action_type": "move", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-sample-1/45.webp", "action_value_1": [666, 414], "thought": "停止按钮触点需要为取反触点，所以我选 Negated，再把变量设为 `Stop_PB`。"}, {"id": 45, "action_type": "move", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-sample-1/46.webp", "action_value_1": [920, 109], "thought": "停止触点已放好。接着在其右侧放置线圈，并把变量指定为 `Motor`。"}, {"id": 46, "action_type": "move", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-sample-1/47.webp", "action_value_1": [749, 557], "thought": "线圈保持普通 Normal，变量选择 `Motor`。"}, {"id": 47, "action_type": "move", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-sample-1/48.webp", "action_value_1": [882, 109], "thought": "主回路的启动触点、停止触点和线圈都放好了。现在在线圈右侧添加 Right PowerRail。"}, {"id": 48, "action_type": "move", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-sample-1/49.webp", "action_value_1": [645, 444], "thought": "母线属性弹窗再次出现，这次改成 Right PowerRail 并确认。"}, {"id": 49, "action_type": "move", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-sample-1/50.webp", "action_value_1": [1064, 109], "thought": "主回路元件已摆放好，但目前还缺少导线连接。我先用连接线工具把左母线接到启动触点，确认连线方式。"}, {"id": 50, "action_type": "move", "image": "static/manifest/data/题目-1442-gpt5.4-sample-1/51.webp", "action_value_1": [730, 605], "thought": "